				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Foresighting technique: &lt;/strong&gt;The technique is generally&lt;strong&gt; applied in calligraphy art.&lt;/strong&gt; It is used in the context where&lt;strong&gt; the letters do not appear too small when you are far away from the calligraphic text or it does not appear too large when you see it from close.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
